Arthur !
Is the cupboard of plate set out ?
All 's in order , sir .
I am in love with my liveries every time I think on 'em ; they
make a gallant show , by my troth . Niece !
Do you call , sir ?
Prithee , show a little diligence , and overlook the knaves a little ;
